reviews.text: What a wonderful find!!! We passed this place one day and decided to look it up on Yelp. The reviews encouraged me to give it a try with some family...

Stopped here Saturday afternoon for a casual lunch. The atmosphere was cool and welcoming, very laid back, and very very clean. 
Walking in, the place...

Best burger I've had in awhile. Smashed burger goodness! 

I've never dined in. Only Door Dash or take out. 

I've only ordered a double Mushroom Swiss but...
